{"tid":229632,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格 : 皇馬已經五年沒能贏得聯賽冠軍了","createTime":"2017-05-04T17:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T05:16:52.000Z","uid":56810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f5c3beb9da6a26d4c14afc902181746a007e905","tid":229632,"uid":56810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"自從阿仙奴跌出前四後，67歲的老帥雲格就成為了球迷抗議的直接對象，而雲格是否會延長他在阿仙奴帥位上的時間也還丞待宣佈。週末輸給北倫敦死敵熱刺後，這樣緊張的氣氛愈發濃烈。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴自2004年後再也沒能奪得過聯賽冠軍，而且被批評為將奪得歐冠盃資格視為成功。現在球隊與聯賽第四名有著6分之差，取得歐冠盃資格的希望已經很小，但雲格再次呼籲人們從困境中展望未來：「如果回顧過去的三年，我們贏得了兩次足總盃，並且分別取得了第二名，第三名和第四名的成績，如今我們又進入了足總盃的決賽。」雲格繼續說道：「總的來說，我能理解大家不滿意的原因是你們想要贏得一切但是你要知道，皇馬已經五年沒能贏得聯賽冠軍了，而利物浦則已經20年沒能奪得聯賽冠軍。我們的對手都是大球會，所以這並不容易。」"},{"pid":"3c58c0e554990f37f9620d0962a55d2fd5f6374d","tid":229632,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/010355_964b6e1f7aecd4ef131826ef486c809c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F010355_964b6e1f7aecd4ef131826ef486c809c.jpg&h=c5803ccd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27b316087b491303eec8a7cfa023eee38c750cc4","tid":229632,"uid":14931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/010355_964b6e1f7aecd4ef131826ef486c809c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F010355_964b6e1f7aecd4ef131826ef486c809c.jpg&h=c5803ccd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7232c9d4e7db95075ca1095a2deaaec8a63140","tid":229632,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"人地有歐聯，你有啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 猁果到駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4f98e27b787508c6ab2168a9b4fd8badedb20d","tid":229632,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"我皇無足總盃，阿&gt;皇"},{"pid":"be3171145f106ac98c69907239429acaddf6bbbf","tid":229632,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我皇無足總盃，阿&gt;皇</blockquote><br />\n人地換左幾多個領隊呀"},{"pid":"f9df107a093f69ff0419620b3f3ba67e80301f15","tid":229632,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"無知一問，想問阿仙奴幾多年冇贏過歐聯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fed956be6d28f8719f0225b186992b2e293bbd0","tid":229632,"uid":33036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"拎皇黎比？ 四年歐聯準備三入決賽啦 4次都有四強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}